805
00:52:09,598 --> 00:52:10,792
l didn't want to bring it up...

806
00:52:10,866 --> 00:52:12,299
l know, it was embarrassing.

807
00:52:13,903 --> 00:52:15,962
You probably thought l was a
drama queen!

808
00:52:17,006 --> 00:52:20,373
No,
l thought you have a lot of guts.

809
00:52:21,977 --> 00:52:22,966
So, everything good now?.
<font face="Palatino Linotype" color="#00ff00"><b>Encoded By CharmeLeon</b></font>

810
00:52:23,879 --> 00:52:24,971
Everything's not good...
<font face="Palatino Linotype" color="#00ff00"><b>Encoded By CharmeLeon</b></font>

811
00:52:25,748 --> 00:52:26,510
but l am.
<font face="Palatino Linotype" color="#00ff00"><b>Encoded By CharmeLeon</b></font>

812
00:52:27,283 --> 00:52:28,511
l have moved on.
<font face="Palatino Linotype" color="#00ff00"><b>Encoded By CharmeLeon</b></font>

813
00:52:29,685 --> 00:52:30,879
And, how's Gayatri?
<font face="Palatino Linotype" color="#00ff00"><b>Encoded By CharmeLeon</b></font>

814
00:52:30,953 --> 00:52:32,818
You know... moved on.

815
00:52:33,889 --> 00:52:34,981
l am so sorry.

816
00:52:35,057 --> 00:52:36,046
Why sorry?

817
00:52:36,325 --> 00:52:37,724
l'm not sorry at all.
<font face="Palatino Linotype" color="#00ff00"><b>Encoded By CharmeLeon</b></font>

818
00:52:38,027 --> 00:52:40,325
Even our drama was
all over the newspapers.

819
00:52:40,396 --> 00:52:41,420
Didn't you read?
<font face="Palatino Linotype" color="#00ff00"><b>Encoded By CharmeLeon</b></font>

820
00:52:42,398 --> 00:52:44,298
l don't read newspapers and magazines.

821
00:52:44,600 --> 00:52:45,396
Why?
<font face="Palatino Linotype" color="#00ff00"><b>Encoded By CharmeLeon</b></font>

822
00:52:45,468 --> 00:52:47,766
Who knows what people
are saying about us!

823
00:52:50,306 --> 00:52:50,795
Cheers to that.

824
00:52:50,840 --> 00:52:51,829
Cheers.

825
00:52:54,009 --> 00:52:58,571
Alex, isn't Mahi looking gorgeous?

826
00:52:59,548 --> 00:53:01,015
She is,
but how does it matter?

827
00:53:01,917 --> 00:53:03,407
Who will sign her?

828
00:53:04,453 --> 00:53:07,854
She's moody, impulsive,
over-emotional.

829
00:53:09,992 --> 00:53:13,359
Alex, whether its
Hollywood or Bollywood...

830
00:53:13,429 --> 00:53:16,489
every legendary actress has
these three qualities.

831
00:53:16,565 --> 00:53:17,031
Oh yeah!

832
00:53:18,434 --> 00:53:19,765
Now, no one can stop her.

833
00:53:20,970 --> 00:53:23,302
Hope she survives.

834
00:53:24,373 --> 00:53:24,998
From whom?

835
00:53:26,575 --> 00:53:27,473
Herself!

836
00:53:29,512 --> 00:53:30,843
Angad, you are crazy!

837
00:53:31,680 --> 00:53:33,375
That's why you and l will get along well.

838
00:53:36,585 --> 00:53:37,779
l think l should leave now.

839
00:53:37,920 --> 00:53:39,319
l just had to be here.

840
00:53:40,289 --> 00:53:41,051
l couldn't help it.

841
00:53:42,791 --> 00:53:46,022
Thank you for rescuing me
from this boring party.

842
00:53:46,529 --> 00:53:47,962
lf you wish,
l can rescue you every day.

843
00:53:49,665 --> 00:53:50,859
What are you doing tomorrow?.

844
00:53:50,933 --> 00:53:52,594
Anyway, whatever you were to do,
cancel it.

845
00:53:53,502 --> 00:53:53,831
Really?

846
00:53:54,303 --> 00:53:56,396
Tomorrow is my cricket match,
you must come.

847
00:53:57,573 --> 00:53:58,631
lt will be fun.

848
00:53:58,707 --> 00:53:59,401
Why?

849
00:53:59,742 --> 00:54:00,299
Why...

850
00:54:01,944 --> 00:54:04,970
Because if you do,
we will definitely win.

851
00:54:07,816 --> 00:54:08,339
l'll think about it.

852
00:54:09,385 --> 00:54:09,942
l'll try.

853
00:54:10,986 --> 00:54:11,918
Good night.

854
00:54:23,799 --> 00:54:25,289
Wow, Mahi!

855
00:54:25,367 --> 00:54:26,766
lnvitation to the match.

856
00:54:26,835 --> 00:54:29,702
That's great publicity.
Clever move.

857
00:54:29,939 --> 00:54:31,531
Pallavi, that wasn't a move.

858
00:54:31,640 --> 00:54:33,608
lf it wasn't, then it should be.

859
00:54:34,476 --> 00:54:35,875
You have to go there tomorrow.

860
00:54:36,478 --> 00:54:37,467
Go to the match.

861
00:54:38,380 --> 00:54:40,940
And make sure
you are seen with him.

862
00:54:42,051 --> 00:54:44,611
Angad Paul is a great catch.

863
00:54:46,355 --> 00:54:48,016
Pallavi, he is a really nice guy.

864
00:54:48,557 --> 00:54:50,923
But to manipulate him...

865
00:54:50,993 --> 00:54:52,358
Mahi Arora...

866
00:54:52,595 --> 00:54:53,687
this is the film industry.

867
00:54:53,862 --> 00:54:57,992
Either you manipulate
or get manipulated.

868
00:54:59,535 --> 00:55:00,763
The choice is yours, babes!

869
00:56:13,375 --> 00:56:14,706
- Thanks, Lobo.
- Your welcome sir.

870
00:56:18,380 --> 00:56:21,406
l was under a lot of pressure before the sixer.

871
00:56:21,650 --> 00:56:22,708
So what did you do?

872
00:56:24,520 --> 00:56:27,580
lf l can't concentrate, l sing.

873
00:56:28,624 --> 00:56:32,458
When the bowler is taking his run-up,
l start singing.

874
00:56:32,528 --> 00:56:34,428
At that time l was singing...

875
00:56:34,496 --> 00:56:36,657
Khoya Khoya Chand...

876
00:56:36,732 --> 00:56:38,427
Khula aasmaan...

877
00:56:40,669 --> 00:56:42,432
...and then took a shot!

878
00:56:42,838 --> 00:56:44,396
You really are mad!

879
00:56:44,873 --> 00:56:49,537
By the way,
my team is grateful to you for my century.

880
00:56:50,379 --> 00:56:50,970
And so am l.

881
00:56:52,014 --> 00:56:53,003
Grateful?

882
00:56:54,583 --> 00:56:55,743
Excuse me.

883
00:56:57,553 --> 00:56:58,042
Yes..

884
00:56:58,353 --> 00:56:59,320
Mahi...

885
00:56:59,388 --> 00:57:01,356
in exactly ten minutes,
leave the restaurant.

886
00:57:01,724 --> 00:57:02,918
And don't forget...

887
00:57:03,525 --> 00:57:03,991
look surprised.

888
00:57:05,494 --> 00:57:06,825
Yes, l will see you soon.

889
00:57:06,895 --> 00:57:08,886
Okay, yeah bye.

890
00:57:11,300 --> 00:57:11,823
What is it?

891
00:57:12,868 --> 00:57:14,358
Nothing. Let's go?

892
00:57:14,536 --> 00:57:15,503
Sure.

893
01:00:19,454 --> 01:00:20,478
Yes, we will meet tomorrow.

894
01:00:20,989 --> 01:00:21,978
Yeah!

895
01:00:28,897 --> 01:00:29,829
Shaguftaji...

896
01:00:32,534 --> 01:00:33,523
how are you?

897
01:00:34,970 --> 01:00:35,902
How are you, Mahi?

898
01:00:36,071 --> 01:00:38,403
l'm alright,
l was shooting on the next floor.

899
01:00:38,473 --> 01:00:38,905
What are you doing here?

900
01:00:39,441 --> 01:00:41,375
l have a shoot on this floor.

901
01:00:42,778 --> 01:00:44,678
Why are you sitting here, in this heat?

902
01:00:44,913 --> 01:00:45,902
Where's your van?

903
01:00:46,581 --> 01:00:47,673
l guess l don't have one.

904
01:00:48,083 --> 01:00:52,543
Since it's only a three day job,
l didn't get one...

905
01:00:52,788 --> 01:00:53,948
You didn't?

906
01:00:56,992 --> 01:00:58,550
- Excuse me!
- Yeah!

907
01:00:58,794 --> 01:01:00,421
- are you from the production team?
- Yes.

908
01:01:00,495 --> 01:01:01,792
Take care of that.

909
01:01:02,030 --> 01:01:02,792
Yes, ma'am.

910
01:01:02,898 --> 01:01:04,490
Where's Shaguftaji's van?

911
01:01:05,267 --> 01:01:07,462
- Don't worry Mahi...
- What do l say!

912
01:01:07,936 --> 01:01:11,463
The producer's wife keeps a tab
on every little thing.

913
01:01:11,907 --> 01:01:14,876
A van for a character artist?
You tell me?

914
01:01:15,477 --> 01:01:16,944
l am helpless.
l am sorry.

915
01:01:18,280 --> 01:01:19,338
Shaguftaji, please come with me...

916
01:01:19,414 --> 01:01:20,438
l'll manage.

917
01:01:20,649 --> 01:01:22,844
When the shot is ready,
you can fetch her from my van.

918
01:01:22,918 --> 01:01:25,409
- Yes, ma'am.
- Shaguftaji, please come.

919
01:01:29,791 --> 01:01:33,420
Mahi, why do you get so upset?

920
01:01:34,529 --> 01:01:36,292
l am used to these things.

921
01:01:36,832 --> 01:01:39,733
We didn't have these vans
when l was a young star.

922
01:01:40,302 --> 01:01:42,998
We would open an umbrella, sit under it...

923
01:01:43,372 --> 01:01:44,737
and start shooting.

924
01:01:47,476 --> 01:01:49,410
lt must've been difficult back then...

925
01:01:49,478 --> 01:01:50,376
no privacy?

926
01:01:50,679 --> 01:01:51,805
l don't know, Mahi.

927
01:01:52,314 --> 01:01:56,045
The entire film unit would
do things together.

928
01:01:56,385 --> 01:02:01,413
Directors, heroes, heroines,
side actors, junior artists...

929
01:02:01,523 --> 01:02:03,718
everyone had a good time.

930
01:02:03,959 --> 01:02:07,690
That's why nothing seemed difficult,
l guess.

931
01:02:08,030 --> 01:02:12,433
ln those days,
relationships were valued a lot.

932
01:02:13,435 --> 01:02:15,960
These days its fame and success.

933
01:02:16,371 --> 01:02:18,635
But don't we become actors
for fame and success?

934
01:02:18,774 --> 01:02:20,002
Yes, we do.

935
01:02:20,442 --> 01:02:21,932
Whatever fame gives us...

936
01:02:22,344 --> 01:02:24,835
it takes away a lot more from us.

937
01:02:25,814 --> 01:02:28,578
We fail to see in the glow of glamour...

938
01:02:29,284 --> 01:02:31,479
how much we have lost.

939
01:02:31,686 --> 01:02:35,679
When we realize it, it's often too late.

940
01:02:41,530 --> 01:02:43,020
Everything is on schedule.

941
01:02:43,298 --> 01:02:44,458
l am so happy, Mahi.

942
01:02:44,866 --> 01:02:46,959
Seven A-list endorsements
in four months.

943
01:02:47,502 --> 01:02:50,528
11 high profile events and
you are on every cover page.

944
01:02:50,806 --> 01:02:51,932
l think we are on the right track.

945
01:02:53,341 --> 01:02:54,399
lt's all thanks to you, Pallavi.

946
01:02:54,609 --> 01:02:57,339
That's all very nice but
you are essentially a heroine.

947
01:02:57,579 --> 01:02:59,444
You have to sign a film.

948
01:03:00,082 --> 01:03:00,912
Rashid bhai!

949
01:03:01,917 --> 01:03:03,350
l think he is absolutely right.

950
01:03:04,286 --> 01:03:07,551
A heroine gets commercials and
endorsements based on her films.

951
01:03:07,789 --> 01:03:09,814
And, it's high time you signed a film.

952
01:03:14,362 --> 01:03:14,885
Abbas Khan...

953
01:03:15,797 --> 01:03:17,424
is making the remake of
a super hit South lndian film.

954
01:03:17,799 --> 01:03:19,027
He's also shooting the entire film abroad.

955
01:03:19,701 --> 01:03:21,498
lf you get this film...

956
01:03:21,937 --> 01:03:22,995
you are home!

957
01:03:24,339 --> 01:03:27,536
But l've heard that
he is considering Rhea Mehra.

958
01:03:28,343 --> 01:03:31,005
Gayatri is also desperate to get it.

959
01:03:32,848 --> 01:03:33,872
So, what are my chances?

960
01:03:34,683 --> 01:03:36,947
We will know the answer to that
only if you try.

961
01:03:37,652 --> 01:03:38,619
lt's very simple.

962
01:03:39,387 --> 01:03:41,651
Either you join Rhea and Gayatri in the race...

963
01:03:41,723 --> 01:03:43,748
and defeat them.

964
01:03:43,825 --> 01:03:45,793
Or sit here and accept defeat.

965
01:03:46,795 --> 01:03:47,693
lt's up to you.

966
01:03:52,300 --> 01:03:52,994
Mind blowing.

967
01:03:53,068 --> 01:03:54,501
Excellent shot.

968
01:03:55,871 --> 01:03:56,667
We will set up for the next shot?

969
01:03:56,738 --> 01:03:57,432
Yes, sure.

970
01:03:57,472 --> 01:03:58,029
Okay!

971
01:04:04,880 --> 01:04:06,541
l'm at a shoot, mom.
Talk to you later.

972
01:04:06,615 --> 01:04:08,845
Just a minute, it's urgent.

973
01:04:09,451 --> 01:04:12,750
Pratap's political party is organizing
a cleanliness drive in Mumbai.

974
01:04:12,821 --> 01:04:15,312
He wants you to attend the event.

975
01:04:15,390 --> 01:04:17,620
Forjust 10 minutes,
as the chief guest.

976
01:04:17,692 --> 01:04:20,388
Tell him to contact Rashid bhai
and to finalize a deal in 2 million.

977
01:04:20,695 --> 01:04:22,720
What? Are you crazy?

978
01:04:22,797 --> 01:04:25,823
You will charge your mother?
That too for a social cause?

979
01:04:26,001 --> 01:04:27,400
Stop over reacting, mom.

980
01:04:27,903 --> 01:04:29,996
lt's the ruling party and they are loaded.

981
01:04:30,805 --> 01:04:32,705
l'm doing it for 2 only for you
otherwise l charge 3 million!

982
01:04:33,008 --> 01:04:33,804
Mahi, please.

983
01:04:33,875 --> 01:04:35,638
l've promised Pratap.
You know...

984
01:04:35,844 --> 01:04:38,039
Mom, l don't have time for this.
We'll talk later.

985
01:04:42,017 --> 01:04:42,881
Surekha, come on.

986
01:04:42,951 --> 01:04:43,440
Yes.

987
01:04:51,359 --> 01:04:55,386
Rhea has been celebrating her
25th birthday for the past five years!

988
01:04:56,598 --> 01:04:57,360
Surekha...

989
01:04:57,866 --> 01:04:59,527
They write such things about every heroine.

990
01:04:59,768 --> 01:05:01,429
No, you don't know.

991
01:05:01,670 --> 01:05:02,864
She is very shrewd.

992
01:05:03,471 --> 01:05:06,702
l know her since she was
a struggling model.

993
01:05:08,009 --> 01:05:11,945
She knows very well how to be at the right place,
at the right time.

994
01:05:12,013 --> 01:05:13,810
She will do anything to achieve her goal.

995
01:05:14,249 --> 01:05:14,772
Madam...

996
01:05:14,950 --> 01:05:15,780
Anything.

997
01:05:17,485 --> 01:05:21,387
She is at least 31 years old.

998
01:05:21,856 --> 01:05:25,724
She forged her age in her
birth certificate and passport.

999
01:05:25,961 --> 01:05:26,655
l know it.

1000
01:05:26,695 --> 01:05:27,684
lt's true.

1001
01:05:28,630 --> 01:05:30,530
Remember the film 'Bad Boys'?

1002
01:05:30,899 --> 01:05:32,867
She made a passport before that film.

1003
01:05:33,401 --> 01:05:35,301
Anyway, what have l got to do with it.

1004
01:05:35,370 --> 01:05:36,701
l like to focus on my job.

1005
01:05:36,871 --> 01:05:39,465
l'm not at all interested in such gossip.

1006
01:05:40,442 --> 01:05:41,306
l forgot something...

1007
01:05:41,376 --> 01:05:42,001
the flowers!

1008
01:05:42,277 --> 01:05:43,437
Madam, l'll get the flowers.

1009
01:05:57,926 --> 01:05:58,415
Hi mom...

1010
01:05:58,994 --> 01:06:01,690
what were you saying about
Pratap Khurana's rally?

1011
01:06:03,565 --> 01:06:06,295
Fine, tell him l will do it.

1012
01:06:07,369 --> 01:06:07,664
Done deal.

1013
01:06:08,637 --> 01:06:13,472
Long live, Pratap Khurana!

1014
01:06:23,852 --> 01:06:26,753
Mahi...

1015
01:06:38,867 --> 01:06:41,495
l request Mahi to say a few words.

1016
01:06:42,904 --> 01:06:43,598
Thank you!

1017
01:06:44,472 --> 01:06:46,997
Actually, l don't know a lot about politics.

1018
01:06:47,742 --> 01:06:48,766
But what l do know is that...

1019
01:06:48,843 --> 01:06:51,676
a cleanliness drive is important for every city.

1020
01:06:52,047 --> 01:06:56,313
l'm happy that Pratapji and the national party
have organized this.

1021
01:06:56,685 --> 01:06:59,677
And l shall begin
the drive from his constituency.

1022
01:07:01,856 --> 01:07:03,653
Say it with me...

1023
01:07:03,725 --> 01:07:08,458
Clean Mumbai, Healthy Mumbai!

1024
01:07:24,546 --> 01:07:25,638
Thanks, Mahi.

1025
01:07:26,581 --> 01:07:30,483
l know film stars get paid a lot
to attend events like this one.

1026
01:07:30,885 --> 01:07:32,682
But you're doing this only for your mother.

1027
01:07:33,388 --> 01:07:34,446
l am really grateful to you.

1028
01:07:35,490 --> 01:07:36,718
Any time, Pratap uncle.

1029
01:07:37,025 --> 01:07:39,755
Let me know if l can ever help in any way.

1030
01:07:39,828 --> 01:07:40,453
Thanks.

1031
01:07:44,632 --> 01:07:46,691
Actually, l'd like a small favor.

1032
01:07:47,001 --> 01:07:47,933
Of course.

1033
01:07:52,440 --> 01:07:54,931
There's this actress, Rhea Mehra.

1034
01:07:55,009 --> 01:07:58,376
She has forged her age in her passport.

1035
01:07:59,314 --> 01:08:02,977
l think, if you could alert the authorities...

1036
01:08:03,385 --> 01:08:05,876
Yes, no problem. l will do that.

1037
01:08:11,626 --> 01:08:12,991
Shinde, hand me the passport.

1038
01:08:15,597 --> 01:08:16,586
What's the matter, officer?

1039
01:08:18,500 --> 01:08:19,933
Madam, you have to come with us.

1040
01:08:20,368 --> 01:08:21,494
But what's the problem?

1041
01:08:21,569 --> 01:08:23,764
We need to question you.
Get her.

1042
01:08:24,806 --> 01:08:25,636
Please come.

1043
01:08:27,375 --> 01:08:29,309
The breaking news at the moment.

1044
01:08:29,778 --> 01:08:34,010
Airport immigration authorities
have detained actress Rhea Mehra...

1045
01:08:34,282 --> 01:08:36,978
for forging her age in her passport.

1046
01:08:37,352 --> 01:08:40,879
Rhea Mehra was on her way to Paris
with her friends to celebrate her birthday.

