01:41:27,472 --> 01:41:30,066
But right now,
l want to concentrate on my career.

1564
01:41:31,075 --> 01:41:32,235
He also has his career.

1565
01:41:33,177 --> 01:41:34,701
What's the rush?

1566
01:41:36,281 --> 01:41:37,111
Mahi...

1567
01:41:38,383 --> 01:41:41,978
whether you marry Angad or not,
is your decision.

1568
01:41:42,887 --> 01:41:45,048
But let me make this clear.

1569
01:41:45,256 --> 01:41:47,952
Tell Angad what's in your heart.

1570
01:41:47,992 --> 01:41:49,186
Don't keep him hanging.

1571
01:41:49,394 --> 01:41:51,988
Don't do to him what Aryan did to you.

1572
01:41:52,664 --> 01:41:53,426
Get it?

1573
01:42:03,374 --> 01:42:04,363
l knew it!

1574
01:42:04,942 --> 01:42:07,240
Everybody told me that you won't marry me.

1575
01:42:07,312 --> 01:42:08,779
l didn't want to accept.

1576
01:42:10,148 --> 01:42:11,877
Try to understand.

1577
01:42:12,283 --> 01:42:14,274
l'm not saying l don't want to marry you.

1578
01:42:14,886 --> 01:42:17,320
All l'm saying is right now we need to
give time to our careers.

1579
01:42:18,122 --> 01:42:19,282
What's the rush?

1580
01:42:22,327 --> 01:42:24,727
You wasted a whole year with that excuse!

1581
01:42:25,997 --> 01:42:27,191
How much more time do you want?

1582
01:42:28,399 --> 01:42:30,993
lt's all nonsense.
Just excuses!

1583
01:42:32,003 --> 01:42:35,097
When you heroines have love,
you chase a career...

1584
01:42:35,173 --> 01:42:36,435
when you make it big, you want love!

1585
01:42:36,908 --> 01:42:38,136
You greedy women!

1586
01:42:39,110 --> 01:42:42,079
lt's not that your career will end
if you were to marry me!

1587
01:42:42,914 --> 01:42:43,938
l was ajerk!

1588
01:42:44,882 --> 01:42:45,746
Angad!

1589
01:42:45,817 --> 01:42:47,648
l thought you were different.

1590
01:42:48,820 --> 01:42:53,416
l thought you weren't happy,
l wanted to rescue you...

1591
01:42:57,929 --> 01:42:59,726
l loved you, Mahi.

1592
01:43:00,031 --> 01:43:01,089
Angad, please!

1593
01:43:02,400 --> 01:43:03,697
Enough is enough!

1594
01:43:05,103 --> 01:43:06,764
l can't do this anymore.

1595
01:43:09,440 --> 01:43:11,806
Actresses like you can't love someone.

1596
01:43:12,744 --> 01:43:14,405
You can only act as if you do.

1597
01:43:15,847 --> 01:43:16,814
Please, relax.

1598
01:43:16,881 --> 01:43:19,042
You only know how to use others.

1599
01:43:21,753 --> 01:43:23,050
l don't want you anymore!

1600
01:43:27,058 --> 01:43:28,389
l don't want you anymore!

1601
01:44:05,863 --> 01:44:06,420
Hello...

1602
01:44:10,101 --> 01:44:10,795
What?!

1603
01:44:10,935 --> 01:44:12,903
Tapanda, you can't do this.

1604
01:44:13,204 --> 01:44:14,296
How can you shelve this film?

1605
01:44:14,372 --> 01:44:15,236
You can't shelve this film.

1606
01:44:15,373 --> 01:44:16,431
l can do anything l want.

1607
01:44:16,974 --> 01:44:18,202
Bloody corporate film makers!

1608
01:44:18,709 --> 01:44:21,405
They're trying to teach a National award
winning director to make a film!

1609
01:44:21,679 --> 01:44:24,807
Sometimes they say the film is serious,
sometimes they want humor.

1610
01:44:24,882 --> 01:44:26,372
They want to add an item number...

1611
01:44:26,717 --> 01:44:28,844
Bloody no aesthetic sense!
Teaching me to make a film!

1612
01:44:28,920 --> 01:44:30,854
l will talk to them. l'll sort everything.

1613
01:44:30,922 --> 01:44:33,220
No, it won't help.

1614
01:44:33,958 --> 01:44:36,085
l've decided l'm not making this film.

1615
01:44:37,395 --> 01:44:37,827
But...

1616
01:44:38,262 --> 01:44:40,321
how can we shelve this film now?.

1617
01:44:41,098 --> 01:44:43,032
Because of this film...

1618
01:44:43,801 --> 01:44:45,735
l sacrificed all other work!

1619
01:44:46,070 --> 01:44:47,935
Now you're walking away from it!

1620
01:44:49,373 --> 01:44:50,032
Mahi!

1621
01:44:50,408 --> 01:44:51,204
Tapanda, please!

1622
01:44:52,910 --> 01:44:54,275
l have lost all patience.

1623
01:44:55,379 --> 01:44:57,779
l know you've put in a lot of effort for this film.

1624
01:44:57,849 --> 01:45:00,977
l know you've sacrificed a lot,
but everything is not lost.

1625
01:45:01,886 --> 01:45:04,150
This experience will...

1626
01:45:04,388 --> 01:45:06,015
make you a better actress.

1627
01:45:06,290 --> 01:45:07,314
Tapanda, please!

1628
01:45:07,725 --> 01:45:09,090
That's when you'll thank me.

1629
01:45:12,263 --> 01:45:12,957
Bless you.

1630
01:45:13,030 --> 01:45:14,895
Tapanda...

1631
01:45:36,420 --> 01:45:38,411
Gracy, just get out.

1632
01:45:38,756 --> 01:45:40,087
Pull the blinds.

1633
01:45:41,692 --> 01:45:42,852
Just go!

1634
01:45:45,863 --> 01:45:46,693
They say...

1635
01:45:46,764 --> 01:45:50,825
to make good friends,
you have to be one yourself.

1636
01:45:50,902 --> 01:45:54,736
Unfortunately film stars can't think of anyone
but themselves.

1637
01:45:56,040 --> 01:45:58,031
lf Mahi had a true friend...

1638
01:45:58,442 --> 01:46:00,467
she wouldn't have been so scared...

1639
01:46:00,745 --> 01:46:02,076
wouldn't have made so many mistakes.

1640
01:46:03,114 --> 01:46:05,480
Tarranum Jaan was a big mistake.

1641
01:46:06,250 --> 01:46:08,184
And Mahi resorted to punishing herself.

1642
01:46:08,853 --> 01:46:09,376
She was ruined.

1643
01:46:10,721 --> 01:46:13,417
Her rivals and newcomers
replaced her.

1644
01:46:14,058 --> 01:46:19,428
Shagufta Rizvi was the only person
with whom Mahi felt at peace.

1645
01:46:20,197 --> 01:46:23,792
When l met her during that time,
l wrote...

1646
01:46:23,935 --> 01:46:26,062
that Mahi had brought
this upon herself.

1647
01:46:27,004 --> 01:46:28,869
lt didn't matter
whose fault it was...

1648
01:46:29,840 --> 01:46:31,398
it still hurt.
