1649
01:46:32,243 --> 01:46:33,210
Poor Mahi.
<font face="Palatino Linotype" color="#00ff00"><b>Encoded By CharmeLeon</b></font>

1650
01:46:33,945 --> 01:46:37,108
The things she did to get rid of her pain.

1651
01:46:38,149 --> 01:46:39,275
So, what have you decided?

1652
01:46:40,017 --> 01:46:41,985
We've heard that you
are seeing a psychiatrist.
<font face="Palatino Linotype" color="#00ff00"><b>Encoded By CharmeLeon</b></font>

1653
01:46:43,387 --> 01:46:48,347
You have also mentioned that
you drink regularly.
<font face="Palatino Linotype" color="#00ff00"><b>Encoded By CharmeLeon</b></font>

1654
01:46:50,761 --> 01:46:51,455
So...

1655
01:46:52,363 --> 01:46:57,266
Having scrutinized your family background
and your professional life...

1656
01:46:57,335 --> 01:46:59,963
the adoption panel has concluded that...

1657
01:47:00,237 --> 01:47:02,762
you are incapable of being a single parent.

1658
01:47:07,044 --> 01:47:08,272
lncapable?

1659
01:47:10,047 --> 01:47:13,278
What do you mean?
How did they decide?

1660
01:47:14,151 --> 01:47:18,281
Have they ever seen me... met me?

1661
01:47:19,357 --> 01:47:22,758
Some forms tell you
l am not capable?!

1662
01:47:23,861 --> 01:47:24,759
Tell me, sister.
<font face="Palatino Linotype" color="#00ff00"><b>Encoded By CharmeLeon</b></font>

1663
01:47:24,962 --> 01:47:25,951
Tell me.

1664
01:47:26,297 --> 01:47:26,854
Mahi...
<font face="Palatino Linotype" color="#00ff00"><b>Encoded By CharmeLeon</b></font>

1665
01:47:29,000 --> 01:47:33,767
To become a good parent,
you need patience and emotional control.

1666
01:47:35,206 --> 01:47:37,766
Qualities which you clearly don't have.

1667
01:47:38,809 --> 01:47:40,777
Practice for a few more years...

1668
01:47:41,879 --> 01:47:42,868
and apply again.

1669
01:47:43,214 --> 01:47:43,873
Good day.

1670
01:47:45,416 --> 01:47:47,907
Sister, you can't do this.

1671
01:47:48,152 --> 01:47:49,881
Sister, you can't do this.

1672
01:47:49,954 --> 01:47:50,750
This is wrong.

1673
01:47:51,122 --> 01:47:52,054
l will sue you.

1674
01:47:52,089 --> 01:47:53,113
Do you understand?!

1675
01:47:54,425 --> 01:47:56,450
Yes, l take psychiatric help...

1676
01:47:56,961 --> 01:47:58,724
Yes l drink, so what?

1677
01:47:58,796 --> 01:47:59,854
Let's go...

1678
01:47:59,964 --> 01:48:00,453
come on!

1679
01:48:00,731 --> 01:48:03,222
So what?
l'm not fit to be a mother?

1680
01:48:03,434 --> 01:48:05,299
Let's go...

1681
01:48:06,871 --> 01:48:07,803
l will sue you!

1682
01:48:13,344 --> 01:48:14,333
Hi Mahi.

1683
01:48:16,480 --> 01:48:17,310
What is this, Pallavi?

1684
01:48:18,449 --> 01:48:19,848
You should be happy.

1685
01:48:20,151 --> 01:48:22,984
So what if you couldn't adopt,
at least you are on the front page.

1686
01:48:23,320 --> 01:48:25,811
You need to pay
to get such coverage.

1687
01:48:26,824 --> 01:48:28,189
What nonsense!

1688
01:48:28,793 --> 01:48:30,488
How could you release
this story without my consent?

1689
01:48:31,195 --> 01:48:32,423
Excuse me?

1690
01:48:33,097 --> 01:48:34,928
Since when do l need your consent?

1691
01:48:36,333 --> 01:48:37,391
You've forgotten the time...

1692
01:48:37,868 --> 01:48:40,496
when l made you sneeze into a storm?

1693
01:48:41,272 --> 01:48:43,365
You didn't object then...
there was no problem.

1694
01:48:46,010 --> 01:48:47,910
Because this is my personal life.

1695
01:48:50,881 --> 01:48:51,779
Wake up, Mahi!

1696
01:48:52,349 --> 01:48:56,046
ln this industry, there's no difference between your
professional and personal life.

1697
01:48:56,821 --> 01:48:57,412
Your life...

1698
01:48:57,822 --> 01:48:58,914
is public property.

1699
01:48:59,190 --> 01:49:01,317
l used it to plan your comeback.

1700
01:49:02,026 --> 01:49:03,994
And now you've ruined it.

1701
01:49:05,763 --> 01:49:08,823
Thanks to my PR skills,
you still make headlines...

1702
01:49:08,899 --> 01:49:11,891
and that makes you interesting.

1703
01:49:12,737 --> 01:49:13,931
What else do you have?

1704
01:49:15,072 --> 01:49:17,336
No films, no relationships...

1705
01:49:18,075 --> 01:49:20,100
actually, nothing!

1706
01:49:25,015 --> 01:49:25,811
Get out!

1707
01:49:27,017 --> 01:49:28,177
Right now!

1708
01:49:28,986 --> 01:49:29,918
You are fired.

1709
01:49:31,388 --> 01:49:33,288
And don't ever show me your bloody face.

1710
01:49:34,091 --> 01:49:34,989
Get out!

1711
01:49:42,733 --> 01:49:43,791
Can't face the truth, can you?

1712
01:49:44,869 --> 01:49:46,131
Someone has rightly said...

1713
01:49:47,037 --> 01:49:50,336
There are people and
then there are actors.

1714
01:49:59,316 --> 01:50:02,308
Mukesh, Mahi has given you
two super hits.

1715
01:50:02,920 --> 01:50:04,285
One with Rohan.

1716
01:50:05,256 --> 01:50:08,191
She deserves to do another film
with you. Please.

1717
01:50:08,359 --> 01:50:10,122
Rashid bhai, you know very well that...

1718
01:50:10,194 --> 01:50:12,890
things in the film industry change every Friday.

1719
01:50:13,798 --> 01:50:16,232
Mahi's last hit was with Abbas.

1720
01:50:16,934 --> 01:50:18,367
And that was a year ago.

1721
01:50:19,069 --> 01:50:21,264
Moreover she's not on good terms
with the heroes.

1722
01:50:21,705 --> 01:50:24,105
Not just me, no hero
would want to work with her.

1723
01:50:24,375 --> 01:50:28,072
Not to forget that crazy phase...

1724
01:50:28,946 --> 01:50:31,312
that film on prostitutes...

1725
01:50:31,982 --> 01:50:33,074
Tarranum Jaan!

1726
01:50:33,484 --> 01:50:34,382
She wasted nine months.

1727
01:50:34,451 --> 01:50:35,145
Nine months!

1728
01:50:36,020 --> 01:50:37,954
ln these nine months so many
fresh faces have been launched.

1729
01:50:38,422 --> 01:50:40,481
The industry waits for no one.

1730
01:50:41,826 --> 01:50:44,886
Mahi is neither professional,
nor a box office success.

1731
01:50:45,696 --> 01:50:47,288
l have a suggestion.

1732
01:50:47,698 --> 01:50:49,757
Tell Mahi to do a reality series.

1733
01:50:50,201 --> 01:50:52,362
Or marry a rich NRl.

1734
01:50:54,171 --> 01:50:55,297
Mukesh, look at this...

1735
01:50:55,940 --> 01:50:57,908
South of France.

1736
01:50:57,975 --> 01:50:58,839
Mind blowing.

1737
01:50:58,909 --> 01:50:59,307
Superb, isn't it?

1738
01:50:59,376 --> 01:51:01,003
Great job, fantastic.

1739
01:51:03,247 --> 01:51:04,805
Alright, Mukesh. See you.

1740
01:51:15,259 --> 01:51:16,021
Mahi...

1741
01:51:17,828 --> 01:51:22,288
the lifespan of a heroine is
quite short in our industry.

1742
01:51:24,101 --> 01:51:28,731
lf you sit here doing nothing,
you'll lose that too.

1743
01:51:31,141 --> 01:51:32,870
What can l do, Rashid bhai?

1744
01:51:33,944 --> 01:51:35,104
Nobody is giving me any work.

1745
01:51:35,913 --> 01:51:40,179
There's a good script,
it's a small budget film.

1746
01:51:40,251 --> 01:51:42,219
The director and producer are new.

1747
01:51:43,687 --> 01:51:44,415
What's that term...

1748
01:51:45,122 --> 01:51:46,885
New wave cinema.

1749
01:51:49,894 --> 01:51:52,294
Shall l fix a meeting?

1750
01:52:00,237 --> 01:52:02,398
There's also an offer
to make an appearance.

1751
01:52:05,676 --> 01:52:08,270
At the wedding of an industrialist's daughter...

1752
01:52:09,213 --> 01:52:12,011
you'll be the bride's friend.

1753
01:52:13,117 --> 01:52:15,312
The money is good.

1754
01:52:16,420 --> 01:52:17,751
What do you say?

1755
01:52:32,870 --> 01:52:33,996
Ladies and gentlemen...

1756
01:52:34,371 --> 01:52:35,463
Here is your seat ma'am.

1757
01:52:36,073 --> 01:52:36,937
Alright!

1758
01:52:37,141 --> 01:52:39,041
Here is your boarding pass.

1759
01:52:39,109 --> 01:52:40,098
Thank you.

1760
01:52:41,211 --> 01:52:42,109
l'll get it for you.

1761
01:52:42,179 --> 01:52:43,111
Thank you.

1762
01:55:04,021 --> 01:55:04,385
Hi...

1763
01:55:08,659 --> 01:55:09,648
Won't you invite me in?

1764
01:55:14,765 --> 01:55:15,424
You look beautiful.

1765
01:55:19,236 --> 01:55:22,672
l know, l have hurt you a lot.

1766
01:55:24,942 --> 01:55:26,671
l often thought about talking to you.

1767
01:55:28,879 --> 01:55:29,846
But l just couldn't.

1768
01:55:31,315 --> 01:55:33,078
Then l saw you on the flight and...

1769
01:55:35,352 --> 01:55:36,785
l realized how much l missed you.

1770
01:55:42,159 --> 01:55:43,319
We were so happy.

1771
01:55:44,895 --> 01:55:45,884
What do you want, Aryan?

1772
01:55:48,065 --> 01:55:49,054
l love you, Mahi.

1773
01:55:54,037 --> 01:55:56,801
After we broke up, l realized that...

1774
01:55:59,877 --> 01:56:00,809
l know what you're thinking.

1775
01:56:02,312 --> 01:56:04,405
After we broke up, l had three affairs.

1776
01:56:06,116 --> 01:56:07,845
You know what...

1777
01:56:10,120 --> 01:56:11,109
l...

1778
01:56:11,188 --> 01:56:13,179
l kept comparing them to you.

1779
01:56:15,492 --> 01:56:16,959
And l was disappointed.

1780
01:56:21,198 --> 01:56:22,722
They were just not like us.

1781
01:56:24,968 --> 01:56:26,230
l really love you, Mahi.

1782
01:56:27,304 --> 01:56:28,828
Why?

1783
01:56:31,909 --> 01:56:32,500
Why now?.

1784
01:56:33,177 --> 01:56:36,943
Because no one ever loved me like you did.

1785
01:56:44,021 --> 01:56:45,215
l know...

1786
01:56:45,289 --> 01:56:47,348
l know all of this seems sudden.

1787
01:56:48,425 --> 01:56:49,357
But, really... think about it.

1788
01:56:50,827 --> 01:56:51,885
We were really good together.

1789
01:57:05,709 --> 01:57:07,108
Please, come on.

1790
01:57:10,247 --> 01:57:12,181
l would've done the same if l were you.

1791
01:57:15,852 --> 01:57:17,251
So, l guess this is it then.

1792
01:57:19,423 --> 01:57:21,152
You are precious, Mahi.

1793
01:57:22,726 --> 01:57:23,192
Take care.

1794
01:57:24,962 --> 01:57:25,428
Aryan.

1795
01:57:39,743 --> 01:57:41,040
l am so sorry...

1796
01:57:42,179 --> 01:57:43,339
l am so sorry.

1797
01:57:46,316 --> 01:57:47,283
l am so sorry.

1798
01:57:52,256 --> 01:57:55,225
ln the battle between the heart and the mind,
the heart has always won.

1799
01:57:55,926 --> 01:57:58,986
ln any case, Mahi never followed her mind.

1800
01:58:00,163 --> 01:58:02,097
Mahi and Aryan patched up...

1801
01:58:02,199 --> 01:58:07,000
and her career restarted
with a small budget film, 'Annie'.

1802
01:58:07,070 --> 01:58:11,166
Aryan was serious about her,
but Mahi was not sure.

1803
01:58:11,241 --> 01:58:14,108
The wounds of her past were still fresh and...

1804
01:58:14,144 --> 01:58:17,341
she found accepting this difficult.

1805
01:58:17,414 --> 01:58:21,043
Though Mahi was living with Aryan,
she wasn't with him.

1806
01:58:27,224 --> 01:58:29,089
Having a rough day, Mahi?

1807
01:58:29,426 --> 01:58:30,450
Not at all.

1808
01:58:32,195 --> 01:58:34,186
l've noticed you don't seem happy...

1809
01:58:34,264 --> 01:58:35,060
not as much as you should.

1810
01:58:37,067 --> 01:58:37,999
Mahi...

1811
01:58:39,069 --> 01:58:40,730
How will l know if you don't tell me?

1812
01:58:42,439 --> 01:58:44,100
l don't know...

1813
01:58:45,809 --> 01:58:47,743
There's this fear that...

1814
01:58:49,780 --> 01:58:51,680
if l'm too happy...

1815
01:58:52,783 --> 01:58:54,182
all this will end.

1816
01:58:56,887 --> 01:58:58,081
The past...

1817
01:58:59,222 --> 01:59:00,917
keeps haunting me.

1818
01:59:04,861 --> 01:59:06,260
Listen, Mahi...

1819
01:59:10,200 --> 01:59:12,031
things need time to heal.

1820
01:59:12,903 --> 01:59:14,302
We need to give some time...

