02:15:55,404 --> 02:15:57,702
Both multiplexes and
single screens are rocking.

2121
02:15:58,741 --> 02:15:59,765
Really?

2122
02:15:59,942 --> 02:16:02,467
We have done it.

2123
02:16:02,845 --> 02:16:03,834
