2178
02:19:52,741 --> 02:19:55,141
Mr. Vikram...

2179
02:19:55,210 --> 02:19:56,734
With the offers pouring in...

2180
02:19:56,812 --> 02:19:59,440
Mahi will be busy for the next two years.

2181
02:19:59,715 --> 02:20:00,238
Right...

2182
02:20:00,316 --> 02:20:03,114
