2185
02:20:09,358 --> 02:20:10,188
There Mahi...

2186
02:20:10,826 --> 02:20:11,986
this is the fact about our industry.

2187
02:20:12,261 --> 02:20:14,991
One success and they are all back.

2188
02:20:19,435 --> 02:20:20,834
Anyway...

2189
02:20:20,903 --> 02:20:23,337
